<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>kẖlyny ạ̉qdr ạ̉bwtk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- kẖlyny ạ̉qdr ạ̉bwtk .. wfdytk brwḥ kẖsẖwʿ
 wạsjd bḥmd lnʿmtk .. wmḥbtk lynạ fy yswʿ
 (kẖlyny ạ̉ʿysẖ ʿmry ạlly bạqy .. ʿ ạlạ̉rḍ lyk
 ykfy̱ ạlly ḍạʿ mn byn ạ̹ydy .. wạnạ ạsmy lyk)2
 ạlqrạr- (yạ ạ̉b yḥbny .. yạ ḥb yrdny)2
 yạ qlb yḍmny .. (yạ rb ạrfʿny lyk)2
 2- kẖlyny ạ̉qdm brạ̉ftk .. ḥyạty lk wkl sẖyʾ
 tẖbt jdẖwry fy krmtk .. nqyny bạlḥq ạlmḍyʾ
 (kẖlyny ạ̉kwn gẖṣn fy msyḥy .. mlyạn tẖmạr
 ạ̉sẖhd brwḥk wbklạmk .. ʿn ạ̹kẖtbạr)2</lyrics>
